elements.label: caption
elements.text: Figure 6: Example layout predictions on selected pages from the DocLayNet test-set. (A, D) exhibit favourable results on colored backgrounds. (B, C) show accurate list-item and paragraph differentiation despite densely-spaced lines. (E) demonstrates good table and figure distinction. (F) shows predictions on a Chinese patent with multiple overlaps, label confusion and missing boxes.
